plot: Cleaning lady Lilly Hansen finds her employer, managing director Martinsen, with a knife in his back. The police is summoned and Chief Inspector Bakker is put on the case, despite suffering...
title: Skulle det dukke opp flere lik, så er det bare å ringe...
